Victorinox Swiss Army is proud to announce the launch of the iconic I.N.O.X. Red watch in collaboration with Lisa Cheng, award-winning ‘Spider Girl’, Hong Kong Women’s Speed Climbing Champion. Lisa’s exemplary dedication to sport makes her the ideal individual to represent the beauty and versatility of I.N.O.X. Red combining fashion and functionality simultaneously.
